atanoprost, Apraclonidine, Neostigmine, Pilocarpine, Physostigmine, Acetylcholine, Bimatoprost, Travoprost, Brinzolamide, Brimonidine, Levobunolol', 'Lixisenatide, Albiglutide, Guar gum, Pramlintide, Sitagliptin, Alogliptin, Liraglutide, Troglitazone, Semaglutide, Linagliptin, Dulaglutide, More', 1767369485);
